:"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c2b7c2d9f62012a936e1c07c8e87c4b124bdf42","tid":589551,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6293c949dea5518a33c31e30135d292bca665405","tid":589551,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6cf8336e069be6e5a8df183b3e1313a9640a09e","tid":589551,"uid":70689,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f10b5ae56bb72edf751d9455583012db52972cfd","tid":589551,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:34:10.000Z","msg":"有邊啲人咁得閒全日廿四小時都可以去票站投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廢老 老綜  新移民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:47:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:50:00.000Z","msg":"香港人喺香港仲係公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一等：中國人，外國人<br />\n二等：蝻<br />\n三等：香港人"},{"pid":"ed8389eac6636e62125a4efe95fa1ba0570008df","tid":589551,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>星期日黎架施主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>施主你星期日放假<br />\n唔係全香港放假<br />\n<br />\n人地耶教教會都開門做生意啦</blockquote><br />\n貧尼只係想指出尋日係星期日<br />\n所以即使仍然有人要返工,<br />\n都唔會剩係得&quot;廢老 老綜  新移民&quot;投票架<br />\n<br />\n如實面對落敗既現實, 先可以對症下藥<br />\n唔好再尋找籍口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a563b990dc3d3436469be4f3520ff00175635ad","tid":589551,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed8389eac6636e62125a4efe95fa1ba0570008df","tid":589551,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>星期日黎架施主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>施主你星期日放假<br />\n唔係全香港放假<br />\n<br />\n人地耶教教會都開門做生意啦</blockquote><br />\n貧尼只係想指出尋日係星期日<br />\n所以即使仍然有人要返工,<br />\n都唔會剩係得&quot;廢老 老綜  新移民&quot;投票架<br />\n<br />\n如實面對落敗既現實, 先可以對症下藥<br />\n唔好再尋找籍口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哩啲係影響將來既政策, 關今次咩事, <br />\ncut晚上時間對要番工 vs 唔洗番工既邊班人影響大啲?<br />\n用你logic cut剩一個鐘投票都係唔會&quot;&quot;剩係得廢老 老綜 新移民投票&quot;<br />\n咁係咪一個鐘都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36c0343809959ee9056063d2c093fd36ac7d215","tid":589551,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a563b990dc3d3436469be4f3520ff00175635ad","tid":589551,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed8389eac6636e62125a4efe95fa1ba0570008df","tid":589551,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>星期日黎架施主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>施主你星期日放假<br />\n唔係全香港放假<br />\n<br />\n人地耶教教會都開門做生意啦</blockquote><br />\n貧尼只係想指出尋日係星期日<br />\n所以即使仍然有人要返工,<br />\n都唔會剩係得&quot;廢老 老綜  新移民&quot;投票架<br />\n<br />\n如實面對落敗既現實, 先可以對症下藥<br />\n唔好再尋找籍口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哩啲係影響將來既政策, 關今次咩事, <br />\ncut晚上時間對要番工 vs 唔洗番工既邊班人影響大啲?<br />\n用你logic cut剩一個鐘投票都係唔會&quot;&quot;剩係得廢老 老綜 新移民投票&quot;<br />\n咁係咪一個鐘都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"得返一個鐘未免太極端 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e001650fcbc42f80f8554f87f78065732101f7","tid":589551,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"成日流流長，有心投嘅話點都吱到時間去一去票站啦，忙過誠仔呀？"},{"pid":"d750db8c5c4c50c94cc8fbd9d5a9bbb9b1e8824f","tid":589551,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:25:29.000Z","msg":"有心投票就應該請假啦"}]}